/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 style=\u0022line-height:1.6;\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-02T18:54:04Z\u0022 title=\u002212/02/2015 06:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 2, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EExtra info\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Val","CreatedById":126227,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-02T18:56:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow my whole post above turned into an Editor box\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick on the text and you can type there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdit:\u003C/strong\u003E The picure in my above post doesn\u0027t seem to show properly. You can glimpse it for a fraction of a second if you refresh the page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/LHNbsFS\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LHNbsFS.png?1\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LHNbsFS.png?1\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;height:310px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-12-03T11:16:02Z\u0022 title=\u002212/03/2015 11:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 3, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}